      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 21:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对拜登产业政策的威胁笼罩亚洲企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/trump-threat-to-biden-s-industrial-policy-hangs-over-asian-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普说，“关税”是他最喜欢的词，他在竞选中打赌高额进口税将迫使制造商将工厂迁往美国。]]></description>
