    <item>
      <title>里夫斯在工党“重建”英国的努力中重振大政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-resurrects-big-state-in-labour-s-bid-to-rebuild-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺，工党十多年来的第一份预算将结束紧缩政策，打破经济停滞的束缚。她提出的计划需要很长时间才能见效，工党需要赢得另一场选举才能获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-resurrects-big-state-in-labour-s-bid-to-rebuild-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
