      <title>西班牙宣布哀悼三天，风暴造成 90 多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/spain-reports-50-dead-after-one-of-the-worst-storms-in-a-century</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙宣布哀悼三天，因为强降雨已造成 90 多人死亡，这已经是该国有史以来最严重的自然灾害之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/spain-reports-50-dead-after-one-of-the-worst-storms-in-a-century</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
